  "description": "Cheolsu, who has been single for 34 years straight and has never even managed to hold a proper conversation with a woman. So of course, he’s spending Christmas alone again. That is, until a strangely packaged box shows up at his house.\nAnd out of it comes… A TALL GUY IN A MAID OUFIT?!\nAs if that isn’t shocking enough, the man casually introduces himself as a “companion robot,” and willy-nilly calling Cheolsu “Master.” He says he’ll take care of all the housework naturally and even provide… more intimate services.\nHold on... Why is he so good at everything? Even that?!\nRaws: https://www.mrblue.com/webtoon/wt_000069985",
